                                <extent>ff. 247 </extent>
                                <foliation>Foliation in Arabic numerals.</foliation>
                            </supportDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
                        <handDesc>
                            <summary>Oriental semi-cursive script.</summary>
                            <handNote scope="sole" script="oriental" rend="semi-cursive">Written by
                                Solomon ben Eleazar ha-Rofe ben Ovadiyah ha-Rofe (see also MS.
                                Pococke 314 and <ref target="/p/m/26tqkq202153v1tpt8vp76p92c">MS.
                                    Pococke 320</ref>).</handNote>
                        </handDesc>
                        <bindingDesc>
                            <p>Brown leather binding, blind-tooled.</p>
                        </bindingDesc>
